rows.label: qst202407_msg0001
rows.name: Why are you even here?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0002
rows.name:
Kountess go bye-bye so we
look for her! Craa!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0003
rows.name:
We hear dirty furballs karried
kountess to Avaritia!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0004
rows.name:
To rescue kountess, we became
kargo and kame here!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0005
rows.name:
Right, I see.
You guys must be really dedicated
to this countess person.

rows.label: qst202407_msg0006
rows.name:
We'd be more than happy to help you
find her. What's her name and what
does she look like?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0007
rows.name: Kountess's name, craa?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0008
rows.name: Guys, do you remember?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0009
rows.name: Can't remember, craa!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0010
rows.name: What was it again?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0011
rows.name:
How can you be looking for someone
when you don't remember them?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0012
rows.name:
Come on, I've gotta be smarter
than THEM!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0013
rows.name: Craa! You look just like kountess!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0014
rows.name:
You want be kountess
and nest with us? Craa!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0015
rows.name: Yikes! No thank you!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0016
rows.name:
Kountess get three meals a day
and unlimited naptime, craa!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0017
rows.name: It sweet deal, yes yes?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0018
rows.name: Hmm...

rows.label: qst202407_msg0019
rows.name: Why not, sounds good!

rows.label: qst202407_msg0020
rows.name: Definitely passing on that, sorry.

rows.label: qst202407_msg0021
rows.name:
What? Ibuki, no!
Have you lost your mind?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0022
rows.name:
We'll bring back the Tirkin countess
and save you from this terrible fate.

rows.label: qst202407_msg0023
rows.name:
Three meals a day and unlimited
naptime? Sounds nice...but, no thanks.

rows.label: qst202407_msg0024
rows.name:
Really?
That krying shame.

rows.label: qst202407_msg0025
rows.name:
Don't suppose there are any clues
to the countess's whereabouts?

rows.label: qst202407_msg0026
rows.name:
Let's see if the mercs can gather
any information for us.

rows.label: qst202407_msg0027
rows.name:
Before we bring her back we have
to figure out where she is, I suppose!
